Hello, my name is **Juarez Monteiro**, I am MSc student in Computer Science at Pontifical Catholic University of Rio Grande do Sul (PUCRS), Brazil, under the supervision of [Prof. Dr. Rodrigo C. Barros](http://lattes.cnpq.br/8172124241767828).
I am currently member of the Research Group on Business Intelligence (GPIN). 
In 2015 I finished my graduation in System Analysis and Development at Instituto Federal do Rio Grande do Sul (IFRS) - Canoas/RS, under the supervision of [Prof. Dr. Rafael C. Pinto](http://lattes.cnpq.br/1024108762297830).
I experienced activities in the area through internship opportunities, where I could developed myself as a professional and relate theory with practice. 
In 2011 I finished my Technician course in Precision Mechanics at Technological Center in Precision Mechanics (CETEMP) - SÃ£o Leopoldo/RS. 


My research is in the field of Artificial Intelligence, particularly in Machine Learning and Deep Learning.


